data.title: French lingerie brand Princesse Tam Tam to be stocked in branches of Uniqlo
data.meta_description: French lingerie brand Princesse Tam Tam will be stocked in key branches of Uniqlo from 13 September, including London's Oxford Street and Regent Street,
data.text:
French lingerie brand Princesse Tam Tam will be stocked in key branches of Uniqlo from 13 September, including London's Oxford Street and Regent Street, and online at uniqlo.com.

Both brands are part of the Fast Retailing group of companies, that also includes premium denim brand J Brand, contemporary brand Theory, Helmut Lang and French apparel retailer Comptoir des Cotonniers.

Princesse Tam Tam had previously been available in the UK via wholesale accounts such as Fenwick and Selfridges, however the brand pulled back from UK wholesale but it retained a UK website.
